commit.message:
CMake: Introduce option URIPARSER_SHARED_LIBS=(ON|OFF)

.. that mimics flag BUILD_SHARED_LIBS and falls back to
BUILD_SHARED_LIBS if available, else defaults to ON.

Related:
https://cmake.org/cmake/help/latest/variable/BUILD_SHARED_LIBS.html
